      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically robust example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with its signature individual throttle bodies. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. To ensure long-term structural and mechanical integrity, the rear subframe has been reinforced and the VANOS system has been professionally overhauled. The chassis benefits from refreshed bushings and a well-sorted suspension that maintains factory geometry while offering sharp turn-in. While the finish shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain remains tight and responsive, offering the visceral, high-RPM performance characteristic of the M-division's peak analog era.",
